        "start": 3,
        "end": 8
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_106_000161",
    "sentence": "是歲遣竇固等征西域，置都護、戊己校尉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "校尉",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 16,
        "end": 18
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_106_000162",
    "sentence": "固等適還而西域叛，殺都護陳睦、戊己校尉關寵。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "校尉",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 17,
        "end": 19
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_106_000163",
    "sentence": "於是大怒，欲復發興討，會秋明帝崩，是思心不容也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_106_000164",
    "sentence": "章帝 建初四年 冬，京都牛大疫。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "四年",
